text: Parenthood is a 1989 American comedy movie directed by Ron Howard and starring Steve Martin, Dianne Wiest, Mary Steenburgen, Jason Robards, Rick Moranis, Tom Hulce, Martha Plimpton, Keanu Reeves, Harley Jane Kozak, Joaquin Phoenix, Kevin Hart, Dennis Dugan. It was distributed by Universal Pictures and was nominated for 2 Academy Awards in 1990. It was spun off into two television adaptions in 1990 and 2010. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1989 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Universal Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by Ron Howard Category:Movies adapted into television series Category:Movies about dysfunctional families Category:Movies about parenting Category:Movies about children Category:Movies set in Missouri
